title: Edith Piaf - The Very Best Of
description:
Do you know that Edith Piaf dedicated the song "No Regrets"
to the French Foreign Legion.   I had a mate once, many
years ago - little Cockney guy - and he&#039;d been in the FFL.
He walked out the front door one morning, after telling his 
missus that he was just nipping out for some cigarettes, and
he didn&#039;t come back for another seven years.   Weird or what.
He&#039;d been in - not sure - think it was Kolwezi, Zaire...
something like that.   Anyway, enjoy the album.
